Package: PopShiftCE
Type: Package
Title: Monte Carlo Conditional Error for Two-Stage Trials with Partial Population Shift
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    c(person(given = "Hao",
             family = "Chen",
             email = "hche2036@uni.sydney.edu.au",
             role = c("aut","cre")))
Description: Implements Monte Carlo-calibrated Conditional Error (CE) for two-stage seamless trials 
    with surrogate-only interim and full-data final analysis under partial population shift 
    (design-fixed mixture prevalence). Includes CE lookup calibration under the joint Stage-1 (X, Y) 
    dependence, a final OLS+HC analysis targeting Delta_marg^dagger = delta + eta * pi_fixed, 
    and simulation helpers.
